{"tid":1545723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特稿：港伊戰如期大球場舉行","createTime":"2019-09-06T04:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:38:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"124d148520c962f4885250bd85e9283fd96ad408","tid":1545723,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20190906/20762990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190906%2F20762990&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=fedebd8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190906%2F20762990&h=20dfda0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20190906/20762990</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年09月06日<br />\n<br />\n特稿：港伊戰如期大球場舉行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190906/large/1567697929_d8e2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190906%2Flarge%2F1567697929_d8e2.gif&h=7a35dc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】足總周四公佈，香港足球代表隊下周二對伊朗的世界盃外圍賽，將按原定安排於香港大球場進行，世界排名23位的伊朗球員正陸續抵港，為賽事進行備戰。<br />\n<br />\n港足將於下周二在世界盃亞洲區次圈外圍賽在香港大球場挑戰「亞洲一哥」伊朗，惟伊朗足總指香港政局動盪，多區都爆發警察與市民的激烈衝突，抗爭者試過堵塞機場，雖然伊朗足總獲港府保證來港的安全，但伊朗足總上周再向亞洲足協提出，希望賽事可移師中立場進行。伊朗共和通訊社報道，形容香港局勢處於「差的狀况」，提及「擔心在機場有示威活動，影響球隊安全及行程」，故伊朗足總已去信亞洲足協，申請對香港的賽事能夠安排在中立場比賽。亞洲足協經過會議後，審視過香港目前的情況，又獲特區政府承諾保證伊朗在港期間安全，民政事務局亦保證伊朗必定可如期離港後確定，賽事不會遷到中立場上演，維持下周二晚上八時在香港大球場如期進行。<br />\n<br />\n足總昨以短訊通知傳媒，指伊朗國家隊球員已經陸續抵港，預計本月10日香港對伊朗的世界盃外圍賽，可照原定安排在香港進行。伊朗的比利時籍教練韋莫斯已於日前公佈出戰香港的23人名單，除現效力俄超辛尼特、有伊朗美斯之稱的阿斯蒙外，陣內還有效力英超白禮頓的查漢巴克殊等，戰力強勁。伊朗因首輪賽事輪空，又未有安排友賽，故球員已分批提早來港準備周二作客香港。<br />\n記者：曾雁平 <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《環時》「篤灰」行動蔓延港球迷會<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n首仗作客和柬埔寨 港隊痛失兩分<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n《環時》「篤灰」行動 蔓延港球迷會"},{"pid":"1ede9ad019eb0e33bc7898ac0a8d90a074efcf8d","tid":1545723,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e7a01eceb875eabe77d40460dbd62d292d5775f","tid":1545723,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:29:02.000Z","msg":"唱香港國歌"},{"pid":"98f74dff4b62be0891cd33d40cd6f05fa081d0af","tid":1545723,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:32:23.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=c28b7ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"0a2b92cc029a998fd6d26ee8c04b27d526a728e8","tid":1545723,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"亞洲呃飯食一哥"},{"pid":"6275ea2af1f010027ce57dd74bab315dac64d01f","tid":1545723,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<